title: [Misun's Weaponry]
[Misun's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a wide-planked white cedar ceiling, a multihued Vornavian silk tapestry hangs on one of the dark blue textured canvas walls.  A low wrought iron table and some wrought-iron hooks sit in opposite corners while a suit of silver-chased armor rests on a white limestone floor.

Beneath a wide-planked white cedar ceiling, a sphere-hilted mounted sword plaque hangs on one of the dark blue textured canvas walls.  A low wrought iron table and some wrought-iron hooks sit in opposite corners while a thin gold-edge black runner rests on a white limestone floor.
